#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1076
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Do you want to add \"%1\" as payee/receiver?\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Ar mhaith leat \"%1\" a chur leis mar íocaí/faighteoir?\n"
"\n"

#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1078
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Selecting \"Yes\" will create the payee, \"No\" will skip creation of a "
"payee record and remove the payee information from this transaction. "
"Selecting \"Cancel\" aborts the import operation.\n"
"\n"
"If you select \"No\" here and mark the \"Do not ask again\" checkbox, the "
"payee information for all following transactions referencing \"%1\" will be "
"removed."
msgstr ""
"Má roghnaíonn tú \"Tá\", cruthófar an t-íocaí, má roghnaíonn tú \"Níl\", "
"seachnófar cruthú taifead an íocaí agus bainfear faisnéis an íocaí ón "
"idirbheart seo. Má roghnaíonn tú \"Cealaigh\", cuirfear deireadh leis an "
"oibríocht allmhairithe.\n"
"\n"
"Má roghnaíonn tú \"Níl\" anseo agus má mharcálann tú an bosca seiceála \"Ná "
"fiafraigh arís\", bainfear faisnéis an íocaí do na hidirbhearta ina dhiaidh "
"sin go léir a thagraíonn do \"%1\"."

