#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1509
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KMyMoney cannot determine which of your accounts to use.  You can create a "
"new account by pressing the <b>Create</b> button or select another one "
"manually from the selection box below."
msgstr ""
"Ní féidir le KMyMoney a chinneadh cé acu de do chuntais atá le húsáid. Is "
"féidir leat cuntas nua a chruthú tríd an gcnaipe <b>Cruthaigh</b> a bhrú nó "
"ceann eile a roghnú de láimh ón mbosca roghnúcháin thíos."

#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1514
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"No account information has been found in the selected statement file. Please "
"select an account using the selection box in the dialog or create a new "
"account by pressing the <b>Create</b> button."
msgstr ""
"Ní bhfuarthas aon fhaisnéis chuntais sa chomhad ráitis roghnaithe. Roghnaigh "
"cuntas ag baint úsáide as an mbosca roghnúcháin sa dialóg nó cruthaigh "
"cuntas nua tríd an gcnaipe <b>Cruthaigh</b> a bhrú."

#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1543
#, kde-format
msgid "Import transactions"
msgstr "Idirbhearta allmhairithe"

#: kmymoney/converter/mymoneystatementreader.cpp:1586
