#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, m_skipStripping)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsonlinequotes.ui:155
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>For easier processing of the data returned by the online source, KMyMoney "
"usually strips unused parts before it is parsed with the regular "
"expressions. If matching of the fields relies on those items, then use this "
"option to turn stripping off.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>The following items are usually removed by stripping:\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li>HTML tags such as <b>&lt;tag&gt;</b></li>\n"
"<li>& encoded characters such as <b>&amp;nbsp;</b></li>\n"
"<li>duplicate whitespace</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Chun próiseáil níos éasca a dhéanamh ar na sonraí a sheolann an fhoinse "
"ar líne, is gnách go mbaintear codanna neamhúsáidte de KMyMoney sula "
"ndéantar iad a pharsáil leis na habairtí rialta. Má bhraitheann meaitseáil "
"na réimsí ar na míreanna sin, bain úsáid as an rogha seo chun an stríocadh a "
"mhúchadh.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>De ghnáth baintear na míreanna seo a leanas trí stríocadh:\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li>Clibeanna HTML ar nós <b>&lt;tag&gt;</b></li>\n"
"<li>& carachtair ionchódaithe ar nós <b>&amp;nbsp;</b></li>\n"
"<li>spás bán dúblach</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"</p>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, m_skipStripping)
