#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton2)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:395
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"Collect all transactions for the given payee. Treat all transactions that "
"refer to the same category and have an amount with +/- X % as identical. If "
"more than one transaction is found, a list of them is presented to the "
"user.\n"
"\n"
"Selecting 0% will list all transactions."
msgstr ""
"Bailigh na hidirbhearta uile don íocaí tugtha. Déan na hidirbhearta uile a "
"bhaineann leis an gcatagóir chéanna agus a bhfuil méid +/- X% acu a mheas "
"mar idirbhearta comhionanna. Má aimsítear níos mó ná idirbheart amháin, "
"cuirtear liosta díobh i láthair don úsáideoir.\n"
"\n"
"Má roghnaítear 0%, liostálfar na hidirbhearta uile."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton2)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:398
#, kde-format
msgid "Same transaction if amount differs less than percentage set below"
msgstr ""
"Idirbheart céanna má tá an méid difriúil níos lú ná an céatadán atá leagtha "
"síos thíos"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton3)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:411
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The data of the last transaction assigned to the category used most often "
"for this payee is autofilled into the transaction editor."
msgstr ""
"Déantar sonraí an idirbhirt dheireanaigh a sannadh don chatagóir is minice a "
"úsáidtear don íocaí seo a líonadh isteach go huathoibríoch san eagarthóir "
"idirbhirt."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, radioButton3)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:414
#, kde-format
msgid "With previously most often used transaction for the payee"
