#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, label)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:433
#, kde-format
msgid "Same transaction if amount differs less than "
msgstr ""
"Idirbheart céanna má tá an difríocht idir an méid agus an méid níos lú ná "

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QSpinBox, kcfg_AutoFillDifference)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:440
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Two transactions are usually treated identical for autofill, if they refer "
"the same accounts. They are treated as different transactions though, when "
"their amount varies by more than the percentage given here."
msgstr ""
"De ghnáth, déantar dhá idirbheart a láimhseáil go comhionann le haghaidh "
"uathlíonta, má bhaineann siad leis na cuntais chéanna. Déantar iad a "
"láimhseáil mar idirbhearta difriúla, áfach, nuair a athraíonn a méid níos mó "
"ná an céatadán a thugtar anseo."

