#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:472
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked the memos from the previous transaction will be "
"used otherwise the memos will not be considered when the transaction is "
"autofilled."
msgstr ""
"Má tá an rogha seo roghnaithe, úsáidfear na meamraim ón idirbheart roimhe "
"sin nó ní chuirfear na meamraim san áireamh nuair a líonfar an t-idirbheart "
"isteach go huathoibríoch."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_AutoFillUseMemos)
#: kmymoney/dialogs/settings/ksettingsregister.ui:475
#, kde-format
