#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel2)
#: kmymoney/plugins/csv/export/csvexportdlg.ui:37
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"From this dialog you are able to export transactions to a comma separated "
"file, (known as a CSV file, because of the extension).  However, you are "
"able to specify an alternative separator below.  Please enter the path to "
"the CSV file or select it by clicking on the Browse button.\n"
"\n"
"You can choose the file's path, and the account. Choose Account to export "
"all the transactions between the specified dates,  or just choose to export "
"Categories."
msgstr ""
"Ón dialóg seo is féidir leat idirbhearta a easpórtáil chuig comhad scartha "
"le camóga, (ar a dtugtar comhad CSV, mar gheall ar an síneadh). Mar sin "
"féin, is féidir leat deighilteoir malartach a shonrú thíos. Cuir isteach an "
"cosán chuig an gcomhad CSV nó roghnaigh é trí chliceáil ar an gcnaipe "
"Brabhsáil.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat cosán an chomhaid agus an cuntas a roghnú. Roghnaigh Cuntas "
"chun na hidirbhearta go léir idir na dátaí sonraithe a easpórtáil, nó "
"roghnaigh Catagóirí a easpórtáil."

