"icalendar.org/iCalendar-RFC-5545/3-6-2-to-do-component.html\">VTODO</a> "
"entries into the iCalendar file but for Google Calendar entries of type <a "
"href=\"https://icalendar.org/iCalendar-RFC-5545/3-6-1-event-component.html"
"\">VEVENT</a> are needed.</p></body></html>"
msgstr ""
"<html><head/><body><p>Scríobh an comhad iCalendar ionas go n-aithneoidh "
