#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, m_skipZero)
#: kmymoney/plugins/views/reports/reporttabgeneral.ui:100
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"              <p>\n"
"              This option is for investments reports only which\n"
"              show prices instead of balances as all other reports do.\n"
"              </p>\n"
"              <p>\n"
"              Select this option to include prices only if there is an "
"actual price for the date.\n"
"              If not, 0 will be shown. In the graph, the value will be "
"skipped.\n"
"              </p>\n"
"              <p>\n"
"              If this option is off the last existing price is shown for a "
"period, if\n"
"              it is on, in a table the value is '0' shown and in a chart a "
"linear\n"
"              interpolation for the missing values will be performed.\n"
"              <br>Example:\n"
"              <br>There are prices for January and March, but there is no "
"price for\n"
"              February.\n"
"              <ul>\n"
"              <li><b>OFF</b>: shows the price for February as the last price "
"of\n"
"              January\n"
"              <li><b>ON</b>: in a table the value is '0', in a chart a "
"linear\n"
"              interpolation for the February-price will be performed\n"
"              (so it makes a kind of average-value using the January- and "
"the\n"
"              March-price in the chart)\n"
"              </ul>\n"
"              </p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"              <p>\n"
"              Níl an rogha seo ach le haghaidh tuarascálacha infheistíochta "
"a thaispeánann \n"
"              praghsanna in ionad iarmhéideanna mar a dhéanann gach "
"tuarascáil eile.\n"
"              </p>\n"
"              <p>\n"
"              Roghnaigh an rogha seo chun praghsanna a áireamh ach amháin má "
"tá\n"
"              praghas iarbhír ann don dáta. Mura bhfuil, taispeánfar 0. Sa "
"ghraf, scipeálfar an luach.\n"
"              </p>\n"
"              <p>\n"
"              Mura bhfuil an rogha seo ann taispeántar an praghas deireanach "
"atá ann cheana\n"
"              féin do thréimhse,  tá sé ar siúl, i dtábla taispeántar an "
"luach '0' agus i gcairt déanfar\n"
"              idir shuíomh líneach do na luachanna atá ar iarraidh.\n"
"              <br>Sampla:\n"
"              <br>Tá praghsanna ann do mhí Eanáir agus mhí an Mhárta, ach "
"níl aon phraghas ann do\n"
"              mhí Feabhra.\n"
"              <ul>\n"
"              <li><b>AS</b>: taispeánann sé praghas mhí Feabhra mar an "
"praghas deireanach de mhí\n"
"              Eanáir\n"
"              <li><b>AR</b>: i dtábla is é an luach '0', i gcairt déanfar "
"idirshuíomh líneach\n"
"              do phraghas mhí Feabhra (mar sin cruthaíonn sé cineál "
"meánluacha ag baint \n"
"              úsáide as praghas mhí Eanáir agus mhí an Mhárta sa chairt)\n"
"              </ul>\n"
"              </p>\n"
"            "

