#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:71
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:83
#, kde-format
msgid "Additional keys"
msgstr "Eochracha breise"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KEditListWidget, kcfg_GpgRecipientList)
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:77
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter the id of the key you want to use for data encryption. This can either "
"be an e-mail address or the hexadecimal key id. In case of the key id do not "
"forget the leading 0x."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach aitheantas na heochrach is mian leat a úsáid le haghaidh "
"criptithe sonraí. Is féidir gur seoladh ríomhphoist nó aitheantas "
"heicsidheachúlach é seo. I gcás aitheantas na heochrach, ná déan dearmad ar "
"an 0x chun tosaigh."

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KLed, m_userKeysFound)
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:95
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This symbol denotes, if the key for the given user id has been found in your "
"keyring. It is green when found, dark otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Léiríonn an tsiombail seo an bhfuil an eochair don aitheantas úsáideora "
"tugtha aimsithe i do eochairfháinne. Bíonn sí glas nuair a aimsítear í, "
"dorcha murach sin."

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KLed, m_recoverKeyFound)
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:138
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This symbol denotes, if the KMyMoney recovery key has been found in your "
"keyring. It is green when found, dark otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Léiríonn an tsiombail seo an bhfuarthas eochair aisghabhála KMyMoney i do "
"fháinne eochrach. Bíonn sí glas nuair a fhaightear í, dorcha murach sin."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2)
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:151
#, kde-format
msgid "Recover Key available in keyring"
msgstr "Eochair Aisghabhála ar fáil san eochairfháinne"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_EncryptRecover)
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:181
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can specify to encrypt the data also with the KMyMoney recover key. Only "
"the core KMyMoney developers are in possession of the respective private key "
"required to read back such encrypted data.<p>\n"
"\n"
"This mechanism is provided for the case that you have lost your key and "
"cannot access your data anymore. With this option activated, the KMyMoney "
"developers can decrypt the data and supply you with it in a readable form. "
"Please be prepared, that you have to answer a few detailed questions about "
"the contents of your data before we will send it out."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat a shonrú go gcripteofar na sonraí leis an eochair aisghabhála "
"KMyMoney freisin. Níl ach ag forbróirí lárnacha KMyMoney an eochair "
"phríobháideach faoi seach atá riachtanach chun na sonraí criptithe sin a "
"léamh ar ais.<p>\n"
"\n"
"Cuirtear an mheicníocht seo ar fáil i gcás go bhfuil d’eochair caillte agat "
"agus nach féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar do shonraí a thuilleadh. Agus an "
"rogha seo gníomhachtaithe, is féidir le forbróirí KMyMoney na sonraí a "
"dhíchriptiú agus iad a sholáthar duit i bhfoirm inléite. Bí ullamh, le do "
"thoil, go gcaithfidh tú cúpla ceist mhionsonraithe a fhreagairt faoi ábhar "
"do shonraí sula seolfaimid amach iad."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_EncryptRecover)
#: kmymoney/plugins/xml/xmlstoragesettings.ui:184
#, kde-format
msgid "Also encrypt with KMyMoney's recover key"
msgstr "Criptigh le heochair aisghabhála KMyMoney freisin"

