#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel6)
#: kmymoney/wizards/endingbalancedlg/checkingstartwizardpage.ui:41
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Reconciling your account ensures your records match those of your "
"institution, and that there are no mistakes on either side. You should "
"reconcile your account whenever you receive a statement from your "
"institution.\n"
"\n"
"All relevant information necessary for this process is usually printed on "
"your statement.\n"
"\n"
"On the next page you will verify that the ending balance matches that on "
"your statement. If not, please modify it.\n"
"\n"
"The starting balance is the sum of your cleared and reconciled transactions."
msgstr ""
"Cinntíonn réiteach do chuntais go bhfuil do thaifid ag teacht le taifid "
"d’institiúide, agus nach bhfuil aon bhotúin ar cheachtar taobh. Ba chóir "
"duit do chuntas a réiteach aon uair a fhaigheann tú ráiteas ó d’institiúid.\n"
"\n"
"De ghnáth bíonn an fhaisnéis ábhartha go léir atá riachtanach don phróiseas "
"seo clóite ar do ráiteas.\n"
"\n"
"Ar an gcéad leathanach eile, fíoróidh tú go bhfuil an t-iarmhéid deiridh ag "
"teacht leis an méid atá ar do ráiteas. Mura bhfuil, déan é a mhodhnú le do "
"thoil.\n"
"\n"
"Is é an t-iarmhéid tosaigh suim d’idirbhearta glanta agus réitithe."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, m_skipIntroPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/endingbalancedlg/checkingstartwizardpage.ui:67
#, kde-format
msgid "Don't show this page again when starting the reconciliation next time."
msgstr ""
"Ná taispeáin an leathanach seo arís nuair a thosóidh tú ar an réiteach an "
"chéad uair eile."

