#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel8)
#: kmymoney/wizards/endingbalancedlg/previouspostponewizardpage.ui:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You have previously postponed the reconciliation of this account. If you "
"have entered charges or interests the last time you started reconciling this "
"account you can modify these in the ledger later on.\n"
"\n"
"It is important, that you continue with the same statement you used when you "
"postponed the reconciliation.\n"
"\n"
"All information you have entered into this wizard will be shown and all "
"transactions that you already cleared are marked with a 'C'."
msgstr ""
"Chuir tú athmhuintearas an chuntais seo ar athló roimhe seo. Má chuir tú "
"muirir nó ús isteach an uair dheireanach a thosaigh tú ag athmhuintearas an "
"chuntais seo, is féidir leat iad seo a mhodhnú sa leabhar mór níos déanaí.\n"
"\n"
"Tá sé tábhachtach go leanfaidh tú ar aghaidh leis an ráiteas céanna a "
"d'úsáid tú nuair a chuir tú an athmhuintearas ar athló.\n"
"\n"
"Taispeánfar an fhaisnéis uile a chuir tú isteach sa draoi seo agus marcálfar "
"le 'C' gach idirbheart a ghlan tú cheana féin."

