"Cuir isteach ainm faoina bhfuil an cuntas seo ar eolas laistigh de KMyMoney."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:67
#, kde-format
msgid "Account type"
msgstr "Cineál cuntais"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyGeneralCombo, m_typeSelection)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:106
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p><b>Checking</b>\n"
"Use the checking account type to manage activities on your checking account "
"e.g. payments, checks and cash card purchases.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Savings</b>\n"
"Use the savings account type to manage activities on your savings account.</"
"p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Credit Card</b>\n"
"Use the credit card account type to manage activities on your credit card.</"
"p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Cash</b>\n"
"\n"
"Use the cash account type to manage activities in your wallet.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Loan</b>\n"
"Use the loan account type to manage amortization loans (e.g. mortgages, car "
"loan, money you lend, private loans etc.).</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Investment</b>\n"
"Use the investment account to manage your stock, mutual fund and other "
"investments.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Asset</b>\n"
"Use the asset account type to manage assets (e.g. your house, car or art "
"collection).</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Liability</b>\n"
"Use the liability account type to manage any type of liability except "
"amortization loans. Use it for taxes you owe or money you borrowed from "
"friends. For amortization loans like mortgages you should create a loan "
"account.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><b>Cuntas Seiceála</b>\n"
"Úsáid an cineál cuntais seiceála chun gníomhaíochtaí ar do chuntas seiceála "
"a bhainistiú m.sh. íocaíochtaí, seiceanna agus ceannacháin cárta airgid.</"
"p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Coigiltis</b>\n"
"Úsáid an cineál cuntais choigiltis chun gníomhaíochtaí ar do chuntas "
"coigiltis a bhainistiú.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Cárta Creidmheasa</b>\n"
"Úsáid an cineál cuntais cárta creidmheasa chun gníomhaíochtaí ar do chárta "
"creidmheasa a bhainistiú.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Airgead Tirim</b>\n"
"\n"
"Úsáid an cineál cuntais airgid chun gníomhaíochtaí i do sparán a bhainistiú."
"</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Iasacht</b>\n"
"Úsáid an cineál cuntais iasachta chun iasachtaí amúchta a bhainistiú (e.g. "
"morgáistí, iasacht gluaisteáin, airgead a thugann tú ar iasacht, iasachtaí "
"príobháideacha srl.).</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Infheistíocht</b>\n"
"Úsáid an cuntas infheistíochta chun do stoc, do chiste frithpháirteach agus "
"infheistíochtaí eile a bhainistiú.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Sócmhainn</b>\n"
"Úsáid an cineál cuntais sócmhainne chun sócmhainní a bhainistiú (e.g. do "
"theach, do charr nó do bhailiúchán ealaíne).</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><b>Dliteanas</b>\n"
"Úsáid an cineál cuntais dliteanais chun aon chineál dliteanais a bhainistiú "
"seachas amúchadh iasachtaí. Bain úsáid as le haghaidh cánacha atá dlite agat "
"nó airgid a fuair tú ar iasacht ó chairde. I gcás iasachtaí amúchta cosúil "
"le morgáistí ba chóir duit cuntas iasachta a chruthú.</p>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyCurrencySelector, m_currencyComboBox)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:129
#, kde-format
msgid "Select the currency in which this account is denominated."
msgstr "Roghnaigh an t-airgeadra ina bhfuil an cuntas seo ainmnithe."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_2)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:152
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:106
#, kde-format
msgid "Opening date"
msgstr "Dáta oscailte"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyDateEdit, m_openingDate)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:166
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The opening date would be the date of the last statement. In case you "
"want to keep track of transactions prior to this date, enter the ending "
"balance and statement date of a prior statement and add all following "
"transactions into KMyMoney. KMyMoney will not allow you to enter or modify "
"transactions prior to this date.</p>\n"
"<p><i>Note</i>: If you do not know the exact amount of the opening balance, "
"enter an estimate. You can change this value later before you reconcile this "
"account for the first time.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Is é dáta an ráitis dheireanaigh an dáta oscailte. Más mian leat súil a "
"choinneáil ar idirbhearta roimh an dáta seo, cuir isteach an t-iarmhéid "
"deiridh agus dáta ráitis roimhe seo agus cuir na hidirbhearta ina dhiaidh "
"sin go léir i KMyMoney. Ní cheadóidh KMyMoney duit idirbhearta roimh an dáta "
"seo a iontráil ná a mhodhnú.</p>\n"
"<p><i>Nóta</i>: Mura bhfuil a fhios agat méid cruinn an iarmhéid oscailte, "
"cuir isteach meastachán. Is féidir leat an luach seo a athrú níos déanaí "
"sula ndéanann tú an cuntas seo a réiteach den chéad uair.</p>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2_2)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, m_openingBalanceLabel)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:173
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:163
#, kde-format
msgid "Opening balance"
msgstr "Iarmhéid oscailte"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (AmountEdit, m_openingBalance)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:193
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The opening balance is the balance of the account when you start using it "
"with KMyMoney. For new accounts this is usually 0 but for existing accounts "
"this may well differ. Please consult the account statements to figure out "
"this value. The opening balance is to be provided in the currency of the "
"account as selected with the currency button.</p>\n"
"<p><i>Note</i>: If you do not know the exact amount of the opening balance, "
"enter an estimate. You can change this value later before you reconcile this "
"account for the first time.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Is é an t-iarmhéid tosaigh iarmhéid an chuntais nuair a thosaíonn tú á "
"úsáid le KMyMoney. I gcás cuntais nua is gnách go mbíonn sé seo 0 ach i gcás "
"cuntais atá ann cheana féin, d'fhéadfadh sé seo a bheith difriúil. Féach ar "
"ráitis an chuntais le do thoil chun an luach seo a fháil amach. Tá an t-"
"iarmhéid tosaigh le soláthar in airgeadra an chuntais mar a roghnaíodh leis "
"an gcnaipe airgeadra.</p>\n"
"<p><i>Nóta</i>: Mura bhfuil a fhios agat méid cruinn an iarmhéid tosaigh, "
"cuir isteach meastachán. Is féidir leat an luach seo a athrú níos déanaí "
"sula ndéanann tú an cuntas seo a réiteach den chéad uair.</p>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, m_conversionLabel)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:203
#, kde-format
msgid "Conversion rate"
msgstr "Ráta comhshó"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (AmountEdit, m_conversionRate)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:216
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"For foreign currencies an initial conversion rate needs to be provided. This "
"should be the price of the foreign currency in the base currency on the "
"opening date of the account."
msgstr ""
"I gcás airgeadraí coigríche, ní mór ráta comhshó tosaigh a sholáthar. Ba "
"chóir gurb é seo praghas an airgeadra coigríche san airgeadra bonn ar dháta "
"oscailte an chuntais."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QPushButton, m_onlineQuote)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:226
#, kde-format
msgid "Online quote"
msgstr "Luachan ar líne"

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, m_preferredAccount)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:259
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Mark this checkbox to include the account in the group of favorite accounts"
msgstr ""
"Marcáil an bosca seiceála seo chun an cuntas a chur san áireamh sa ghrúpa "
"cuntas is fearr leat"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, m_preferredAccount)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:262
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Selecting the <b>Favorite Account</b> checkbox will allow preferred access "
"to this account in some dialogs and views of KMyMoney."
msgstr ""
"Trí an bosca seiceála <b>Cuntas Is Fearr Leat</b> a roghnú, beidh rochtain "
"tosaíochta agat ar an gcuntas seo i roinnt dialóga agus radhairc de KMyMoney."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, m_preferredAccount)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kaccounttypepage.ui:265
#, kde-format
msgid "Favorite account"
msgstr "Cuntas is fearr leat"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel14)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kbrokeragepage.ui:27
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Does this investment account have a brokerage account?<p>\n"
"\n"
"<b>Check</b> the mark if this investment account has an associated account "
"for money that is not invested.<br>\n"
"\n"
"<b>Uncheck</b> it if you do not use this account for active stock brokerage. "
"You should also uncheck it if the account is not maintained by a bank or "
"broker."
msgstr ""
"An bhfuil cuntas bróicéireachta ag an gcuntas infheistíochta seo?<p>\n"
"\n"
"<b>Seiceáil</b> an marc má tá cuntas gaolmhar leis an gcuntas infheistíochta "
"seo le haghaidh airgid nach bhfuil infheistithe.<br>\n"
"\n"
"<b>Díthiceáil</b> é mura n-úsáideann tú an cuntas seo le haghaidh "
"bróicéireachta stoic ghníomhach. Ba chóir duit é a dhíthiceáil freisin mura "
"bhfuil an cuntas á chothabháil ag banc nó bróicéir."

