#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:58
#, kde-format
msgid "Who is the payee/payer of the loan?"
msgstr "Cé hé/hí íocóir na hiasachta?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyPayeeCombo, m_payee)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:70
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter the name of the person or bank you owe money or who owes you money.\n"
"\n"
"If the name does not exist within KMyMoney's database, you are asked if you "
"want to create it."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach ainm an duine nó an bhainc a bhfuil airgead dlite agat dó nó a "
"bhfuil airgead dlite duit.\n"
"\n"
"Mura bhfuil an t-ainm ann i mbunachar sonraí KMyMoney, iarrtar ort an mian "
"leat é a chruthú."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:77
#, kde-format
msgid "Did you make/receive any payments yet?"
msgstr "An ndearna/an bhfuair tú aon íocaíochtaí fós?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KComboBox, m_anyPayments)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:89
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Were there any payments for this loan whether they are entered into KMyMoney "
"or not?\n"
"\n"
"Note: Payments made to obtain the loan (e.g. Disagio) are not considered as "
"payments in this context."
msgstr ""
"An raibh aon íocaíochtaí ann don iasacht seo, bíodh siad curtha isteach i "
"KMyMoney nó ná bíodh?\n"
"\n"
"Nóta: Ní mheastar gur íocaíochtaí sa chomhthéacs seo íocaíochtaí a rinneadh "
"chun an iasacht a fháil (e.g. Disagio)."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_anyPayments)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:93
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item no payments were entered for a loan"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Ní raibh"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_anyPayments)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:98
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item payments were entered for a loan"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Bhí"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:106
#, kde-format
msgid "Which payments do you want to record?"
msgstr "Cé na híocaíochtaí ar mhaith leat a thaifeadadh?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KComboBox, m_recordings)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:121
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt>Select which transactions should be recorded.\n"
"\n"
"<b>All payments</b> allows you to enter all payments made for this loan.\n"
"\n"
"The option to <b>start from the beginning of the current year</b> is meant "
"for loans that have already been active for a longer period of time, and for "
"which you do not want to enter all past transactions.\n"
"</qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt>Roghnaigh cé na hidirbhearta ba chóir a thaifeadadh.\n"
"\n"
"Ligeann <b>Gach íocaíocht</b> duit na híocaíochtaí uile a rinneadh don "
"iasacht seo a iontráil.\n"
"\n"
"Tá an rogha <b>tosú ó thús na bliana reatha</b> beartaithe d'iasachtaí atá "
"gníomhach cheana féin ar feadh tréimhse níos faide, agus nach mian leat na "
"hidirbhearta uile san am atá thart a iontráil ina leith.\n"
"</qt>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_recordings)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:125
#, kde-format
msgid "All payments"
msgstr "Gach íocaíocht"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), item, widget (KComboBox, m_recordings)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:130
#, kde-format
msgid "Start with this year's payments"
msgstr "Tosaigh le híocaíochtaí na bliana seo"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:138
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter the ending balance found on the statement that is the last one before "
"you want to start recording this loan in KMyMoney."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach an t-iarmhéid deiridh atá le fáil ar an ráiteas deireanach sula "
"dteastaíonn uait an iasacht seo a thaifeadadh i KMyMoney."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1_3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kgeneralloaninfopage.ui:141
#, kde-format
msgid "Balance before start of recording"
