#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kinstitutionpage.ui:27
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If this account is managed by an institution please select the institution "
"from the list. If the institution does not exist yet, please choose the "
"<b>New Institution</b> button to create it. Otherwise, leave this field "
"empty.\n"
"Enter the account number used by the institution to identify the account."
msgstr ""
"Más é institiúid atá i mbun bainistíochta ar an gcuntas seo, roghnaigh an "
"institiúid ón liosta. Mura bhfuil an institiúid ann fós, roghnaigh an cnaipe "
"<b>Institiúid Nua</b> chun í a chruthú. Seachas sin, fág an réimse seo "
"folamh.\n"
"Cuir isteach an uimhir chuntais a úsáideann an institiúid chun an cuntas a "
"aithint."

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KComboBox, m_institutionComboBox)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kinstitutionpage.ui:54
#, kde-format
msgid "Select the institution which manages this account or leave empty"
msgstr "Roghnaigh an institiúid a bhainistíonn an cuntas seo nó fág folamh é"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QPushButton, m_newInstitutionButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kinstitutionpage.ui:61
#, kde-format
msgid "New Institution"
msgstr "Institiúid Nua"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KLineEdit, m_accountNumber)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kinstitutionpage.ui:80
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Accounts managed by an institution are usually referenced by a unique number "
"the so called account number. Enter that number here.\n"
"\n"
"KMyMoney currently uses this number only for some online banking functions."
msgstr ""
"De ghnáth, tagraítear do chuntais a bhainistíonn institiúid le huimhir "
"uathúil, ar a dtugtar uimhir chuntais. Cuir isteach an uimhir sin anseo.\n"
"\n"
"Ní úsáideann KMyMoney an uimhir seo ach le haghaidh roinnt feidhmeanna "
"baincéireachta ar líne faoi láthair."

#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (KLineEdit, m_iban)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kinstitutionpage.ui:97
#, kde-format
msgid "Enter the International Bank Account Number into this field"
msgstr "Cuir isteach Uimhir Chuntais Bhainc Idirnáisiúnta sa réimse seo"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KLineEdit, m_iban)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kinstitutionpage.ui:104
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can enter the IBAN (International Bank Account Number) into this field "
"if you know it. Usually, people at your institution can tell you the number "
"or it is printed on your statements.\n"
"\n"
"See also https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Bank_Account_Number for "
"more information.\n"
"\n"
"KMyMoney keeps this field only for documentation purposes and does not use "
"it otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an IBAN (Uimhir Chuntais Bhainc Idirnáisiúnta) a iontráil sa "
"réimse seo má tá a fhios agat í. De ghnáth, is féidir le daoine i "
"d'institiúid an uimhir a insint duit nó bíonn sí priontáilte ar do ráitis.\n"
"\n"
"Féach freisin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"International_Bank_Account_Number le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais.\n"
"\n"
"Ní choinníonn KMyMoney an réimse seo ach chun críocha doiciméadaithe agus ní "
"úsáideann sé é ar aon bhealach eile."

