#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.ui:23
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Now enter the details for your loan. You can leave one of the fields empty "
"and KMyMoney will calculate it when you press the <b>Calculate</b> button. "
"Before you can continue with the next page you also need to press "
"<b>Calculate</b> so that KMyMoney can check the logical correctness of the "
"values you have supplied."
msgstr ""
"Anois cuir isteach sonraí d'iasachta. Is féidir leat ceann de na réimsí a "
"fhágáil folamh agus ríomhfaidh KMyMoney é nuair a bhrúnn tú an cnaipe "
"<b>Ríomh</b>. Sula bhféadann tú leanúint ar aghaidh leis an gcéad leathanach "
"eile ní mór duit <b>Ríomh</b> a bhrú freisin ionas gur féidir le KMyMoney "
"ceart loighciúil na luachanna atá curtha ar fáil agat a sheiceáil."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel7)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newaccountwizard/kloandetailspage.ui:53
#, kde-format
