#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWizardPage, DurationWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/durationwizardpage.ui:6
#, kde-format
msgid "Duration"
msgstr "Aga"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel15_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/durationwizardpage.ui:13
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Please enter the term of this loan or leave the field empty to calculate it. "
"The term is the time that is required to fully repay the loan. This time "
"might be different from the time your loan contract is signed for."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Cuir isteach téarma na hiasachta seo nó fág an réimse folamh chun é a ríomh. "
"Is é an téarma an t-am a theastaíonn chun an iasacht a aisíoc go hiomlán. "
"D’fhéadfadh an t-am seo a bheith difriúil ón am a síníodh do chonradh "
"iasachta."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel1_1_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editintrowizardpage.ui:43
#, kde-format
msgid "Edit Loan Account Wizard"
msgstr "Draoi Cuir Chuntas Iasachta in Eagar"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel1_2_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editintrowizardpage.ui:77
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Welcome to the Edit Loan Account Wizard. Please use this wizard to modify "
"information about your loan account.\n"
"\n"
"Please make sure that you have the relevant information handy. You usually "
"get the information out of your contract and the last statement."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Fáilte go dtí an Draoi um Chur in Eagar Cuntas Iasachta. Bain úsáid as an "
"draoi seo le do thoil chun faisnéis faoi do chuntas iasachta a mhodhnú.\n"
"\n"
"Déan cinnte go bhfuil an fhaisnéis ábhartha ar láimh agat. De ghnáth, "
"gheobhaidh tú an fhaisnéis as do chonradh agus as an ráiteas deireanach."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QWizardPage, EditSelectionWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Edit selection"
msgstr "Cuir rogha in eagar"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel2_2_1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:27
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Please select, which data of the loan you want to modify."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Roghnaigh, le do thoil, cé na sonraí den iasacht is mian leat a mhodhnú."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_editInterestRateButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:95
#, kde-format
msgid "Modify the interest rate"
msgstr "Modhnaigh an ráta úis"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_editOtherCostButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:105
#, kde-format
msgid "Modify additional fees"
msgstr "Modhnaigh táillí breise"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_editOtherInfoButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:115
#, kde-format
msgid "Modify other loan information"
msgstr "Modhnaigh faisnéis iasachta eile"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_editAttributesButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/editselectionwizardpage.ui:125
#, kde-format
msgid "Modify loan attributes"
msgstr "Athraigh tréithe iasachta"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/effectivedatewizardpage.cpp:44
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Please enter the date from which on the following changes will be effective. "
"The date entered must be later than the opening date of this account (%1), "
"but must not be in the future. The default will be today."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach an dáta óna mbeidh na hathruithe seo a leanas i bhfeidhm. Ní "
"mór don dáta a chuirtear isteach a bheith níos déanaí ná dáta oscailte an "
"chuntais seo (%1), ach ní féidir leis a bheith sa todhchaí. Is é an dáta "
"réamhshocraithe inniu."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QWizardPage, EffectiveDateWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/effectivedatewizardpage.ui:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Effective date"
msgstr "Dáta éifeachtach"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel1_7)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/effectivedatewizardpage.ui:94
#, kde-format
msgid "When should the changes become active?"
msgstr "Cathain ba chóir na hathruithe a bheith gníomhach?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel17_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/finalpaymentwizardpage.ui:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Please enter the amount of a final amortization payment or leave the field "
"empty to calculate it."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Cuir isteach méid na híocaíochta amúchta deiridh nó fág an réimse folamh "
"chun é a ríomh."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/firstpaymentwizardpage.cpp:49
#, kde-format
msgid "Please enter the date, the first payment for this loan was/is due."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach an dáta, le do thoil, a raibh/tá an chéad íocaíocht don iasacht "
"seo dlite."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/firstpaymentwizardpage.cpp:51
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Note: Consult the loan contract for details of the first due date. Keep in "
"mind, that the first due date usually differs from the date the contract was "
"signed"
msgstr ""
"Nóta: Féach ar an gconradh iasachta le haghaidh sonraí faoin gcéad dáta "
"dlite. Coinnigh i gcuimhne, go mbíonn an chéad dáta dlite difriúil de ghnáth "
"ón dáta a síníodh an conradh"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/firstpaymentwizardpage.cpp:55
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Please enter the date, the first payment for this loan was/is due this year."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach an dáta le do thoil, bhí/tá an chéad íocaíocht don iasacht seo "
"dlite i mbliana."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/firstpaymentwizardpage.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Note: You can easily figure out the date of the first payment if you consult "
"the last statement of last year."
msgstr ""
"Nóta: Is féidir leat dáta na chéad íocaíochta a dhéanamh amach go héasca má "
"fhéachann tú ar an ráiteas deireanach den bhliain seo caite."

#. i18n: ectx: property (title), widget (QWizardPage, FirstPaymentWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/firstpaymentwizardpage.ui:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Date of first payment"
msgstr "Dáta na chéad íocaíochta"

#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWizardPage, InterestCalculationWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestcalculationwizardpage.ui:6
#, kde-format
msgid "Interest calculation"
msgstr "Ríomh úis"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel12_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestcalculationwizardpage.ui:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"When does the actual interest rate get calculated?"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Cathain a ríomhtar an ráta úis iarbhír?"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_interestOnReceptionButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestcalculationwizardpage.ui:68
#, kde-format
msgid "When the payment is received."
msgstr "Nuair a fhaightear an íocaíocht."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_interestOnPaymentButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestcalculationwizardpage.ui:78
#, kde-format
msgid "When the payment is due."
msgstr "Nuair a bheidh an íocaíocht dlite."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestcategorywizardpage.cpp:49
#, kde-format
msgid "Create a new category"
msgstr "Cruthaigh catagóir nua"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestcategorywizardpage.cpp:50
#, kde-format
msgid "Use this to open the new account editor"
msgstr "Úsáid é seo chun an eagarthóir cuntais nua a oscailt"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel20_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestcategorywizardpage.ui:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Please select the category you want to assign the interest payments to or "
"create a new category."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Roghnaigh an chatagóir ar mhaith leat na híocaíochtaí úis a shannadh di nó "
"cruthaigh catagóir nua."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel5_4)
#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel14_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interesteditwizardpage.ui:19
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interestwizardpage.ui:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Please enter the interest rate or leave the field empty to calculate it."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Cuir isteach an ráta úis nó fág an réimse folamh le go ríomhfar é."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel7_3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interesteditwizardpage.ui:93
#, kde-format
msgid "Current rate"
msgstr "Ráta reatha"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel9_4)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interesteditwizardpage.ui:151
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KMyMoney either calculates the new interest rate or the amount for principal "
"and interest. If you know the interest rate then enter it here.\n"
"\n"
"If KMyMoney should calculate this value for you, then leave the field blank."
msgstr ""
"Ríomhann KMyMoney an ráta úis nua nó an méid don phríomhshuim agus don ús. "
"Má tá an ráta úis ar eolas agat, cuir isteach anseo é.\n"
"\n"
"Más mian le KMyMoney an luach seo a ríomh duit, fág an réimse bán."

#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWizardPage, InterestTypeWizardPage)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interesttypewizardpage.ui:6
#, kde-format
msgid "Type of interest"
msgstr "Cineál spéise"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel5_2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interesttypewizardpage.ui:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Is the interest of this loan fixed over a period of time or is it adapted "
"from time to time? If the interest rate changes during the amortization "
"phase of the loan you should choose the option 'variable interest rate'."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"An bhfuil ús na hiasachta seo socraithe thar thréimhse ama nó an ndéantar é "
"a oiriúnú ó am go ham? Má athraíonn an ráta úis le linn chéim amúchta na "
"hiasachta, ba cheart duit an rogha 'ráta úis athraitheach' a roghnú."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_fixedInterestButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interesttypewizardpage.ui:68
#, kde-format
msgid "Fixed interest rate"
msgstr "Ráta úis seasta"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, m_variableInterestButton)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/interesttypewizardpage.ui:78
#, kde-format
msgid "Variable interest rate"
msgstr "Ráta úis athraitheach"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/keditloanwizard.cpp:77
#, kde-format
msgid "Edit loan wizard"
msgstr "Draoi iasachta a chur in eagar"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/keditloanwizard.cpp:93
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Note: you will not be able to modify this account today, because the opening "
"date \"%1\" is in the future. Please revisit this dialog when the time has "
"come."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara: ní bheidh tú in ann an cuntas seo a mhodhnú inniu, mar "
"go bhfuil an dáta oscailte \"%1\" sa todhchaí. Tabhair cuairt ar an dialóg "
"seo arís nuair a bheidh an t-am tagtha."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/keditloanwizard.cpp:281
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Your previous selection was \"%1\". If you select another option, KMyMoney "
"will dismiss the changes you have just entered. Do you wish to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Ba é \"%1\" an rogha a rinne tú roimhe seo. Má roghnaíonn tú rogha eile, "
"cuirfidh KMyMoney na hathruithe atá díreach curtha isteach agat ar neamhní. "
"Ar mhaith leat dul ar aghaidh?"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/keditloanwizard.cpp:286
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "Confirmation"
msgstr "Deimhniú"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:72
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The loan wizard is unable to calculate two different values for your loan at "
"the same time. Please enter a value for the %1 on this page or backup to the "
"page where the current value to be calculated is defined and fill in a value."
msgstr ""
"Ní féidir leis an draoi iasachta dhá luach éagsúla a ríomh do d'iasacht ag "
"an am céanna. Cuir isteach luach don %1 ar an leathanach seo nó téigh ar ais "
"chuig an leathanach ina bhfuil an luach reatha atá le ríomh sainmhínithe "
"agus líon isteach luach."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:106
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You selected, that payments have already been made towards this loan. This "
"requires you to enter the loan amount exactly as found on your last "
"statement."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh tú go bhfuil íocaíochtaí déanta cheana féin i leith an iasachta "
"seo. Éilíonn sé seo ort méid an iasachta a iontráil díreach mar a bhí sé le "
"fáil ar do ráiteas deireanach."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:116
#, kde-format
msgid "interest rate"
msgstr "ráta úis"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgid "term"
msgstr "téarma"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.cpp:131
#, kde-format
msgid "principal and interest"
msgstr "príomhshuim agus ús"

#. i18n: ectx: property (windowTitle), widget (QWizard, KNewLoanWizard)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard.ui:23
#, kde-format
msgid "New Loan Wizard"
msgstr "Draoi Iasachtaí Nua"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:144
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:161
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:178
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:195
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:213
#, kde-format
msgid "calculate"
msgstr "ríomh"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:334
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The number of payments has been decremented and the final payment has been "
"modified to %1."
msgstr ""
"Tá líon na n-íocaíochtaí laghdaithe agus tá an íocaíocht dheireanach "
"athraithe go %1."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:341
#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:359
#, kde-format
msgid "The final payment has been modified to %1."
msgstr "Tá an íocaíocht dheireanach athraithe go %1."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newloanwizard/knewloanwizard_p.h:390
#, kde-format
