"can modify it later."
msgstr ""
"Tá cód bainc ag gach institiúid, ar a dtugtar uimhir ródaithe sna Stáit "
"Aontaithe nó cód sórtála sa Ríocht Aontaithe. Cuir isteach anseo é. Mura "
"bhfuil tú cinnte, fág an réimse bán. Is féidir leat é a mhodhnú níos déanaí."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:72
#, kde-format
msgid "Name of the institution"
msgstr "Ainm na hinstitiúide"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KLineEdit, m_accountNumberEdit)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:92
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"In general the institution that issued the account also issued a number for "
"it. Enter it here. If uncertain, you can modify this entry later."
msgstr ""
"Go ginearálta, d’eisigh an institiúid a d’eisigh an cuntas uimhir dó "
"freisin. Cuir isteach anseo í. Mura bhfuil tú cinnte, is féidir leat an "
"iontráil seo a mhodhnú níos déanaí."

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KLineEdit, m_accountNameEdit)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:99
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter a descriptive name that will be used by KMyMoney to identify your "
"checking account."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach ainm tuairisciúil a úsáidfidh KMyMoney chun do chuntas seiceála "
"a aithint."

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (KMyMoneyDateEdit, m_openingDateEdit)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter the date from when on you plan to keep track of the transactions in "
"that account. This is usually the date of the last statement. If uncertain, "
"leave as is."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach an dáta ar a bhfuil sé beartaithe agat súil a choinneáil ar na "
"hidirbhearta sa chuntas sin. De ghnáth is é seo dáta an ráitis dheireanaigh. "
"Mura bhfuil tú cinnte, fág mar atá."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:143
#, kde-format
msgid "Number of the account"
msgstr "Uimhir an chuntais"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:153
#, kde-format
msgid "Name of the account"
msgstr "Ainm an chuntais"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (AmountEdit, m_openingBalanceEdit)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:185
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Enter the opening balance of the account. This is usually the ending balance "
"of the last statement. If uncertain, leave as is."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach iarmhéid tosaigh an chuntais. De ghnáth is é seo iarmhéid "
"deiridh an ráitis dheireanaigh. Mura bhfuil tú cinnte, fág mar atá."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kaccountpage.ui:216
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The fields below allow you to enter some information about your checking "
"account. Once this wizard finishes, the account will be created for you "
"within KMyMoney."
msgstr ""
"Ligeann na réimsí thíos duit roinnt eolais a iontráil faoi do chuntas "
"seiceála. Nuair a bheidh an draoi seo críochnaithe, cruthófar an cuntas duit "
"laistigh de KMyMoney."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel3)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kcurrencypage.ui:23
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KMyMoney supports multiple currencies. Your reports will be based on a "
"default currency which you can select here. The default for new accounts is "
"also the currency you select here."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn KMyMoney le hairgeadraí iolracha. Beidh do thuairiscí bunaithe ar "
"airgeadra réamhshocraithe ar féidir leat a roghnú anseo. Is é an t-airgeadra "
"réamhshocraithe do chuntais nua an t-airgeadra a roghnaíonn tú anseo freisin."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kgeneralpage.ui:22
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Please enter some information about yourself.<br><br>\n"
"\n"
"This information will be seen and used only by you. The information is used "
"to personalize KMyMoney, to encrypt your file, etc."
msgstr ""
"Cuir isteach roinnt eolais fút féin le do thoil.<br><br>\n"
"\n"
"Ní fheicfidh ach tusa an fhaisnéis seo agus ní úsáidfidh sé í. Úsáidtear an "
"fhaisnéis chun KMyMoney a phearsantú, chun do chomhad a chriptiú, srl."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel7)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kgeneralpage.ui:104
#: kmymoney/wizards/wizardpages/userinfo.ui:104
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label email address"
msgid "Email:"
msgstr "Ríomhphost:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, TextLabel5)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kgeneralpage.ui:165
#, kde-format
msgid "Zip code"
msgstr "Cód poist"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, textLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kintropage.ui:26
#, kde-format
msgid "Welcome to KMyMoney!"
msgstr "Fáilte go KMyMoney!"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kintropage.ui:41
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You have started KMyMoney for the first time on this computer. Before this "
"program can help you to manage your finances, it needs to collect some data "
"from you.<p>\n"
"\n"
"On the next few pages you will be guided through the steps necessary to "
"setup the program. This will happen only once."
msgstr ""
"Tá KMyMoney tosaithe agat den chéad uair ar an ríomhaire seo. Sula féidir "
"leis an gclár seo cabhrú leat do chuid airgeadais a bhainistiú, ní mór dó "
"roinnt sonraí a bhailiú uait.<p>\n"
"\n"
"Ar na chéad chúpla leathanach eile, treorófar tú trí na céimeanna is gá chun "
"an clár a chur ar bun. Ní tharlóidh sé seo ach uair amháin."

#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/knewuserwizard.cpp:53
#, kde-format
msgid "KMyMoney New File Setup"
msgstr "Socrú Comhaid Nua KMyMoney"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/knewuserwizard.cpp:55
#, kde-format
msgctxt "New file wizard introduction"
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Réamhrá"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/knewuserwizard.cpp:56
#, kde-format
msgid "Personal Data"
msgstr "Sonraí Pearsanta"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/knewuserwizard.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgid "Select Currency"
msgstr "Roghnaigh Airgeadra"

#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/knewuserwizard.cpp:58
#, kde-format
msgid "Select Accounts"
msgstr "Roghnaigh Cuntais"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kpasswordpage.ui:23
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>KMyMoney can encrypt your datafile using GPG Encryption. GPG encryption "
"is one of the most secure methods in the world for protecting data. All of "
"your account numbers and other important financial information will be very "
"secure.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Is féidir le KMyMoney do chomhad sonraí a chriptiú ag baint úsáide as "
"Criptiú GPG. Tá criptiú GPG ar cheann de na modhanna is sláine ar domhan "
"chun sonraí a chosaint. Beidh do chuid uimhreacha cuntais agus faisnéis "
"airgeadais thábhachtach eile an-slán.</p>"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kpreferencepage.ui:20
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If you would like to review or change any preference settings for KMyMoney "
"after finishing this wizard, you can do so by checking this box. If not just "
"click <b>Next</b>."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat aon socruithe sainroghanna do KMyMoney a athbhreithniú nó a "
"athrú tar éis duit an draoi seo a chríochnú, is féidir leat é sin a dhéanamh "
"tríd an mbosca seo a sheiceáil. Mura bhfuil, cliceáil ar <b>Ar Aghaidh</b>."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, m_openConfigAfterFinished)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kpreferencepage.ui:32
#, kde-format
msgid "Configure preferences after finishing the wizard."
msgstr "Cumraigh roghanna tar éis duit an draoi a chríochnú."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/newuserwizard/kpreferencepage.ui:60
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can change the configuration options at any time using the configuration "
"dialog. Just select the <b>Configure KMyMoney...</b> option in the "
"<b>Settings</b> menu."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat na roghanna cumraíochta a athrú am ar bith ag baint úsáide as "
"an dialóg chumraíochta. Níl le déanamh ach an rogha <b>Cumraigh KMyMoney...</"
"b> a roghnú sa roghchlár <b>Socruithe</b>."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel2)
#: kmymoney/wizards/wizardpages/accounts.ui:17
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Select groups of accounts that correspond to the ways that you will use "
"KMyMoney. Each group you select will cause several accounts and categories "
"to be created. Select the groups that are relevant to you. You can always "
"create additional accounts manually later."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh grúpaí cuntas a fhreagraíonn do na bealaí a n-úsáidfidh tú "
"KMyMoney. Cruthófar roinnt cuntas agus catagóirí le gach grúpa a roghnaíonn "
"tú. Roghnaigh na grúpaí is ábhartha duit. Is féidir leat cuntais bhreise a "
"chruthú de láimh níos déanaí."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/wizardpages/currency.ui:17
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid ""
"KMyMoney supports multiple currencies, nevertheless one of them will be used "
"as your base currency. The base currency is used as default for new accounts "
"and reports. Please select the base currency from the following list."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn KMyMoney le roinnt airgeadraí, ach úsáidfear ceann acu mar "
"d'airgeadra bonn. Úsáidtear an t-airgeadra bonn mar réamhshocrú do chuntais "
"agus tuarascálacha nua. Roghnaigh an t-airgeadra bonn ón liosta seo a leanas "
"le do thoil."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QTreeWidget, m_currencyList)
#: kmymoney/wizards/wizardpages/currency.ui:36
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "ISO Code"
msgstr "Cód ISO"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QTreeWidget, m_currencyList)
#: kmymoney/wizards/wizardpages/currency.ui:41
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Symbol"
msgstr "Siombail"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, qLabel1)
#: kmymoney/wizards/wizardpages/userinfo.ui:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Use the fields below to enter some information about yourself.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>All information is optional and only used to personalize your KMyMoney "
"file.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Úsáid na réimsí thíos chun roinnt eolais fút féin a iontráil.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>Is rogha an fhaisnéis uile agus ní úsáidtear í ach chun do chomhad "
"KMyMoney a phearsantú.</p>"

#: tools/kmmreport-export.cpp:115
